    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required gradation levels for Model Risk Level 2. Discretization error factor exceeds requirement (achieved gradation 3 vs. required 2). Six factors appropriately scoped to gradation 1 per MRL 2 assessment matrix. Experimental comparison demonstrates NIH predictions within measurement uncertainty. The CFD model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal pump under CPB conditions as specified in COU1.",
